        public abstract  fetch(IBMDataFile.IBMDATAFILE_REQUEST_POLICY policy)
        The fetch method is a provisional API. APIs that are marked provisional are evolving and might change or be removed in future releases. Download file in the background. If using the IBMDataFileRequestReturnCachedIfExists request policy, the download will check for a local copy first. If one exists, it will load the local copy. If not, it will load from the cloud.
